[recv] {"type": "turn_end", "message": {"role": "assistant", "content": [{"type": "thinking", "thinking": "**Considering class coverage**\n\nI'm thinking about whether we need to ensure class coverage. I wonder if that involves assessing schedules or content requirements. I can imagine needing to fill in gaps for specific subjects or manage unexpected absences. Maybe I should check if there are any specific classes that are currently short-staffed or need extra resources? It's important to provide the right support for students, so I want to make sure we’re fully covered across the board!", "thinkingSignature": "{\"id\":\"rs_003a136a710f0758016a252386c2788193aaf3836f333e05ec\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"content\":[],\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABqJSOIqGld0yNSTQQ8Ko2Bh4xnwMI3mMUAEjTmfB4EYe0_5RnkFT7gvc_VckARHsR14dJzYnhO-HqtvLncM1GHtciNmt0L_mF2QZo7fTTVP5_v67B6ilWEf2RVHTmZiq1PSPlnEDVPFqwVr_zeQP75Bd7W0UK4wpvxNmLFL0p_OxaadWKUvnkAQMmlWICQqHBh-U367MWt8FwOiH62KN_zPWhStkfP950DWxFYd2rLb0SnMI0Txa-N0VAyFgZDpLFpVBzu2tkGat7sH-sV9JnHegrKY35RIK-jRN4k6KyNQZAY8Yrfc_M66urQj6MnTUYKz2yosCevz5vtRRmFSntqebPEh5bxAVvu6OhvHLV8LyVntvJexoJ7RE6CwKmPs92PZ3lPFwDW-f9A187pib_hKEXvh4CbPt4wQcax9ZF5xhm4gyeJndDjY4j2WeGoCNrxDUJIV1DjOsIEdHx4v_HewdRfhamlBV3BwdChekM6K8gjsjUhfTU_KaNBhThrBvN7R7mD8hJ8-B1bANBLvkzW_6Kdt0cmx2oWMdkK7BYPfIj0RFwVHfE-y0lb9Z_kTAj7K6M71UtDGl2skJ3-a6EBd4xw4hwPM3oSBKF86GSQMi-kTVNzyuegWZzOL4l_qEZdgyBIJlkcwSxUG-aaA7OuhjSHgQX4ovL7A5KrN1q3rGtHSm_OWlpCDy95obFFmFFHJTsTsV0xlaU3r1fECeH9-Xp8SMHcVYi7u2V0VDoAgzQENgnywnQtL1KmFDuuQ53X2GrFbLVjVWwTeNs5OIsIswzkj_37pbNAKmuv7qQZT0gRFJHqu5Ubbpe9aeclmK_to3WjZih1Q2_Ryy_-nGtLNqcAvaRLA-9pXpgPaqNykZdKc9fvEs6i1IXdgGyQe0cAatR1XkNoWYx8mfjw631G6VlgKtNxhbYAYLTorIFNKRsKNvxcOBhDAzBLoP3z2l5iUuFHK84Y67wLfzd6Vz5A4d2Pqg==\",\"summary\":[{\"type\":\"summary_text\",\"text\":\"**Considering class coverage**\\n\\nI'm thinking about whether we need to ensure class coverage. I wonder if that involves assessing schedules or content requirements. I can imagine needing to fill in g