[recv] {"type": "message_end", "message": {"role": "assistant", "content": [{"type": "thinking", "thinking": "**Analyzing Gradle and JavaAgent usage**\n\nI’m noting that Gradle native doesn't support JavaAgent, but there's coverage in the JVM. I could use the `build.gradle` file to add a configuration that locates the agent jar and uses `test.jvmArgs \"-javaagent:${...}\"`. However, testing in native could be tricky since JUnit tests wouldn’t have instrumentation, which might lead to failures with `fromInstalledAgent`. It’s definitely a catch I need to consider!", "thinkingSignature": "{\"id\":\"rs_003a136a710f0758016a2523f0cc9c8193bd98bdee29ef8cab\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"content\":[],\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABqJSQVvYiChD6cgEmKVLJJ6nvuvQhqUEVLdcCHqAuuLGGMr1nvxggXALE-Udm6h4XZrmFNRMC1NeBPp_w9jke_Bwtx4NKjh0UwjIN7_cYd0PprWDsZMv1Ct_YwQXz78ZurJiPbhUEl20lOEsfbngHJe601R-wYEWBOHAo1hvXsBzZstX5kHovtOAGYxETPKXlzWlK4Rh-ANShuhTSL8Ew0MvnlZCFZEocZGSkgdoQOgbnI9zYtju6E7ZvZiNOZrJn3aTVamHRRDbu50ZkeP0XbuYANH5nJMiQmt5ydAPXiANMW1tQBz4ZnZN2vx6x3WsgqsMlIlDPHLOfmwlzu8FMnAyO4-Do2z97d-Fo92n5CfuLtfpIxlyM7DJZUJQKaXvmkdfhkGLqZ-MqPf_a5agsWsWo5psuZ5MsX_RqV9qwCFGTHL73-7ViXPpRZq4wmskbl0Ml5mxYxtt7ziEr-8FSfzZERC2SvoA_MroQ02HBz34n8RhhrESX-V8o2r3Qvs7OK_6GhMtRc9WDlSh9CZuLnxwJn-BJiioZIHFymNzXYLtalHBVzcF3mGcJ-ZIEh6vHlmqIZUFGQHtRGaN2lfwsNCGEYwqYZgIanSmQL7DXPLEgbgmp7fDaBpaOzKpR7ftegAVwjkBekF343giC2vImuipjfgdT4qTh2AC6rOgeUqvYMqOBUMrki36YUJpaTAcj1uatlWtfB_cTjjvw_62dRaSo3mKCtHF146XDp1nNuLGkaSMAVTlsHNGV7yj3lggtFVXpccQ8nOMZLngU8_mB0Sgd6UlVbdZ2ga8HhScLjgl-tEsqixLL2v4MGfc6OZYYS-zGetHem3dzcLsBAwJ5idsev06Mj-B8mMQI8UkCBZI1qaYvqGvC4l5eNvOLtS4XLevj9Hl7i39sE-DnJA5VP8nYqLbxGofpcQ5x-AA0j9x3LjwyW4AouRs_UEL6Q0TwqQh41Fhpyhpggc9B1lWeGsRMAEdbVNRxk613i1DIaY6QI6um6o6uAbeF7BVhAWR8lHfB22Lb1-vuS8WbNYMyupX9jF0KSPSQ_THQ6oIXwYOAM7PMAYk79LBc_x-p1yWxdsEHOE0XzEmopCn5HdqZm9G4P2ocXUSItOkiAF8ysw6swxyB3OLNAgKW2q7B2eJ8F5C7PhJLMUKEJZjvZZJPaUGoEubkX05j9N1NknPuMh6fd_whnJOLA2IhRj_2LIKEd8SlsMTJMbcMJnKXBTC-5vw3eNX7yZ0_PuO1c93a6ZZLPw418HYZwOm0